      { name: "Teddy's Bigger Burgers (Kailua)", price: 12, rating: 4.7, cuisine: "Burgers", tip: "Hawaii's beloved burger chain. The Big Kahuna burger with grilled pineapple and teriyaki is the essential order." , desc: "Hawaiian burger chain famous for the Big Kahuna — a beef patty topped with grilled pineapple and teriyaki.", photo: "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/20260314_Vkusno_i_Tochka_burger_%2816293%29.jpg/960px-20260314_Vkusno_i_Tochka_burger_%2816293%29.jpg"},
      { name: "Down to Earth (Honolulu)", price: 10, rating: 4.6, cuisine: "Vegan/Vegetarian", tip: "Best vegetarian food in Hawaii. Hot bar is excellent value. Ka'u veggie plate is a local staple." , desc: "Hawaii's top organic and natural grocery with a beloved vegetarian hot bar lunch.", photo: "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/94/Salad_platter.jpg/800px-Salad_platter.jpg"},
      { name: "Roy's Hawaii Kai (Honolulu)", price: 65, rating: 4.8, cuisine: "Hawaiian Fusion", tip: "Roy Yamaguchi's original flagship since 1988. The misoyaki butterfish is a 35-year signature dish." , desc: "Roy Yamaguchi's original restaurant where Hawaiian fusion cuisine was invented in 1988.", photo: "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
      { name: "Zippy's Chili (Honolulu)", price: 8, rating: 4.6, cuisine: "Local Diner", tip: "Hawaii's beloved 24/7 diner chain. The Zip Pac bento and the chili rice are institutions. Open Christmas." , desc: "Hawaii's beloved 24-hour diner chain with a unique local chili recipe and the iconic Zip Pac bento.", photo: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-XCj0Y0xHStM?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"},
        {"name":"Giovanni's Shrimp Truck","price":15,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"Arrive early as the line grows fast and they often sell out by early afternoon.","desc":"Legendary North Shore shrimp truck famous for its garlicky scampi plates served straight from the truck window.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg/800px-Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg"},
        {"name":"Romy's Kahuku Prawns & Shrimp","price":17,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"Try the spicy shrimp option and grab extra napkins — it's delightfully messy.","desc":"Family-run roadside shrimp stand in Kahuku serving fresh farm-raised prawns in savory buttered plates.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b1/Nephrops_norvegicus.jpg/800px-Nephrops_norvegicus.jpg"},
        {"name":"Fumi's Kahuku Shrimp","price":14,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"The coconut shrimp plate is a must-try and pairs perfectly with the included rice.","desc":"Popular yellow shrimp truck on the North Shore known for generous portions and coconut-crusted shrimp.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Oysters_p1040741.jpg/800px-Oysters_p1040741.jpg"},
        {"name":"Macky's Sweet Shrimp","price":16,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"Ask for extra sauce on the side to dip your shrimp for maximum flavor.","desc":"Beloved North Shore shrimp truck specializing in sweet and buttery shrimp plates with mac salad.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg/800px-Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kahuku Shrimp & Prawns","price":13,"rating":4.4,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"The lemon butter shrimp plate is a lighter option great for those who prefer mild flavors.","desc":"No-frills shrimp truck offering classic Hawaiian shrimp plates at wallet-friendly prices with outdoor seating.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Oysters_p1040741.jpg/800px-Oysters_p1040741.jpg"},
        {"name":"North Shore Shrimp Co.","price":18,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"Get there before noon for the freshest catch and the shortest wait times.","desc":"Upscale truck experience offering sustainably sourced shrimp plates with creative island-inspired sauces.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Oysters_p1040741.jpg/800px-Oysters_p1040741.jpg"},
        {"name":"Aloha Shrimp Shack","price":15,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"The garlic butter version with extra chili flakes is the local favorite order.","desc":"Charming roadside shack dishing up heaping shrimp plates with house-made sauces and fresh pineapple slices.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Spicy_fried_King_Prawns.jpg/800px-Spicy_fried_King_Prawns.jpg"},
        {"name":"Sunset Shrimp Truck","price":14,"rating":4.4,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"Visit at sunset for a stunning backdrop to your meal on the beachside picnic tables.","desc":"Scenic shrimp truck parked near Sunset Beach serving classic plates with views of the famous surf break.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Oysters_p1040741.jpg/800px-Oysters_p1040741.jpg"},
        {"name":"Island Garlic Shrimp","price":16,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Shrimp Plate","tip":"The double-garlic upgrade is worth every extra penny for serious garlic lovers.","desc":"Popular shrimp stand known for its ultra-garlicky plates and perfectly seasoned two-scoop rice.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg/800px-Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg"},
        {"name":"Nico's Pier 38","price":22,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Arrive right when they open to snag fresh catch before the daily supply runs out.","desc":"Harborside seafood restaurant at the fishing pier offering some of the freshest fish plates on Oahu.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg/960px-Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg"},
        {"name":"Buzz's Original Steak House","price":38,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"The fresh catch of the day special is always the best value on the menu.","desc":"Classic Lanikai institution serving fresh local fish and seafood with sweeping ocean and mountain views.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg/960px-Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kona Brewing Co. Kailua-Kona","price":28,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Pair the grilled mahi-mahi with a cold Pipeline Porter for the ultimate island experience.","desc":"Beloved Big Island brewery with a full seafood menu featuring locally caught fish alongside craft beers.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Food_Series_%28Home-made%29_of_Mooncake_%28Mid-autumn%29_Festival_-_4th_Crabs_Dish_wanted_to_join.jpg/960px-Food_Series_%28Home-made%29_of_Mooncake_%28Mid-autumn%29_Festival_-_4th_Crabs_Dish_wanted_to_join.jpg"},
        {"name":"Fish Express Lihue","price":18,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Order the poke bowls as an appetizer before diving into the hot seafood plates.","desc":"Kauai's go-to fish market and restaurant where the fish is delivered directly from the boats daily.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg/960px-Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg"},
        {"name":"Merriman's Waimea","price":45,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Reserve a window table well in advance for panoramic views of the Big Island coastline.","desc":"Farm-to-table pioneer restaurant sourcing 90% local ingredients and serving exceptional fresh Hawaiian seafood.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg/960px-Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg"},
        {"name":"The Shrimp Station","price":20,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"The coconut cream shrimp is a dessert-like treat that seafood lovers should never skip.","desc":"Kauai roadside gem serving fresh seafood plates and creative shrimp preparations in a laid-back outdoor setting.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Dinner_02_11_2019_Mussels%2C_Calimari%2C_Prawns_%26_Chorizo_in_a_spicy_tomato_sauce_on_Linguine_with_parmesan._%2849007855028%29.jpg/960px-Dinner_02_11_2019_Mussels%2C_Calimari%2C_Prawns_%26_Chorizo_in_a_spicy_tomato_sauce_on_Linguine_with_parmesan._%2849007855028%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Duke's Waikiki","price":35,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Request a beachfront table and enjoy live Hawaiian music while dining on fresh catch.","desc":"Iconic Waikiki Beach restaurant honoring Duke Kahanamoku with fresh island seafood and stunning sunset views.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Dinner_02_11_2019_Mussels%2C_Calimari%2C_Prawns_%26_Chorizo_in_a_spicy_tomato_sauce_on_Linguine_with_parmesan._%2849007855028%29.jpg/960px-Dinner_02_11_2019_Mussels%2C_Calimari%2C_Prawns_%26_Chorizo_in_a_spicy_tomato_sauce_on_Linguine_with_parmesan._%2849007855028%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Hanalei Dolphin Restaurant","price":42,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Ask the server which fish was caught that morning for the absolute freshest preparation.","desc":"Romantic Kauai riverside restaurant serving fresh-caught fish and seafood steps from the Hanalei River.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Dinner_02_11_2019_Mussels%2C_Calimari%2C_Prawns_%26_Chorizo_in_a_spicy_tomato_sauce_on_Linguine_with_parmesan._%2849007855028%29.jpg/960px-Dinner_02_11_2019_Mussels%2C_Calimari%2C_Prawns_%26_Chorizo_in_a_spicy_tomato_sauce_on_Linguine_with_parmesan._%2849007855028%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Mama's Fish House","price":65,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"Book reservations months ahead as this Maui legend is booked solid nearly every night of the year.","desc":"Maui's most celebrated seafood destination, naming each fish on the menu after the fisherman who caught it.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/80/Airline_meal_asiana.jpg/960px-Airline_meal_asiana.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ono Seafood","price":16,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Fresh Seafood","tip":"This tiny shop has a line out the door so go on weekdays for a shorter wait.","desc":"Tiny Honolulu seafood counter celebrated for some of the best fresh poke and ahi bowls in the city.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg/960px-Garnelen_in_Toast_3.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ahi & Vegetable","price":14,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"Get the spicy ahi with extra seaweed salad on top for the most balanced bite.","desc":"Trendy Honolulu poke shop with build-your-own bowls featuring sushi-grade ahi and creative island toppings.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Sashimi_-_Maguro_Restaurant%2C_Bangna%2C_Bangkok_%2844856596864%29.jpg/800px-Sashimi_-_Maguro_Restaurant%2C_Bangna%2C_Bangkok_%2844856596864%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Pokéworks Honolulu","price":16,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"The wasabi aioli sauce is an underrated gem — ask for it even if it is not listed.","desc":"Fast-casual poke chain that started in Hawaii, known for fresh fish and customizable bowl combinations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/21/Tuna_assortment.png"},
        {"name":"Foodland Farms Poke Counter","price":12,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"Visit in the morning when they restock the freshest cuts and the selection is at its peak.","desc":"Local grocery chain's legendary poke counter offering dozens of styles beloved by both locals and visitors.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/21/Tuna_assortment.png"},
        {"name":"Tamura's Fine Wine & Liquors","price":11,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"The shoyu ahi is the classic fan favorite but the garlic crab poke is worth trying.","desc":"Unassuming liquor store with a cult-status poke counter consistently ranked as the best on Oahu.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Soy_sauce_2.jpg/800px-Soy_sauce_2.jpg"},
        {"name":"Poke to the Max","price":15,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"The brown rice base with limu and onion seasoning is the most authentic local preparation.","desc":"Hawaiian-born poke bowl concept offering generous portions with fresh fish and innovative island flavor profiles.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Sashimi_-_Maguro_Restaurant%2C_Bangna%2C_Bangkok_%2844856596864%29.jpg/800px-Sashimi_-_Maguro_Restaurant%2C_Bangna%2C_Bangkok_%2844856596864%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Island Brew Coffeehouse Poke","price":17,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"Pair your poke bowl with their cold brew made from Kona beans for a perfect island combo.","desc":"Unique Kona coffee shop that doubles as a fresh poke bowl destination with views of the harbor.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Soy_sauce_2.jpg/800px-Soy_sauce_2.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ono Seafood Poke Bar","price":14,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"The octopus poke is an adventurous choice that regulars swear is the best on the island.","desc":"No-frills Kaimuki poke institution serving perfectly seasoned bowls from a tiny counter to devoted regulars.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Soy_sauce_2.jpg/800px-Soy_sauce_2.jpg"},
        {"name":"Fresh Catch Poke","price":13,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"Order the mixed plate with two proteins to get the best tasting sampler experience.","desc":"Local neighborhood poke shop in Kailua serving daily-fresh fish bowls with house-made sauces and toppings.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Sashimi_-_Maguro_Restaurant%2C_Bangna%2C_Bangkok_%2844856596864%29.jpg/800px-Sashimi_-_Maguro_Restaurant%2C_Bangna%2C_Bangkok_%2844856596864%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Alicia's Market","price":10,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"The furikake salmon is a sleeper hit that locals often order over the more famous ahi.","desc":"Hidden gem neighborhood market in Kalihi with a dedicated poke counter that rivals any specialty shop.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Soy_sauce_2.jpg/800px-Soy_sauce_2.jpg"},
        {"name":"Umeke's Fish Market","price":15,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Poke","tip":"The limu poke with sweet onions is the most traditionally Hawaiian preparation on the menu.","desc":"Big Island poke specialist in Kailua-Kona known for its authentic Hawaiian-style preparations and fresh local fish.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Soy_sauce_2.jpg/800px-Soy_sauce_2.jpg"},
        {"name":"Leonard's Bakery","price":8,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"Get the hot malasadas fresh out of the fryer right when they open for the best texture.","desc":"Honolulu's most iconic bakery, famous since 1952 for its warm Portuguese malasadas rolled in cinnamon sugar.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Liliha Bakery","price":7,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"The coco puffs with chantilly cream filling are the item everyone needs to try at least once.","desc":"Old-school Honolulu bakery open since 1950, beloved for its legendary coco puffs and local pastries.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Tropical Dreams Ice Cream & Bakery","price":9,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"The liliko'i cheesecake bar is a tropical spin on a classic that you can only find in Hawaii.","desc":"Big Island artisan bakery crafting pastries with locally grown tropical fruits and Kona coffee flavors.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Punalu'u Bake Shop","price":6,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"The sweet bread in every flavor makes an ideal edible souvenir to bring home from the Big Island.","desc":"The southernmost bakery in the USA, famous for Hawaiian sweet bread baked fresh daily near the black sand beach.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Waiola Shave Ice & Bakery","price":8,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"Pair shave ice with one of their fresh-baked mochi muffins for a truly local snack combination.","desc":"Cherished Honolulu institution combining fresh-baked local pastries with the island's most celebrated shave ice.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Sweet Cakes Bakery Maui","price":10,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"Pre-order custom cakes online as walk-in stock sells out quickly on weekends.","desc":"Maui's favorite custom cake shop and daily bakery serving creative tropical-flavored cakes and pastries.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Aloha Bakehouse","price":9,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"The taro bread is a unique Hawaiian staple that makes an excellent breakfast toasted with butter.","desc":"Artisan Kauai bakery specializing in hearth-baked taro breads, seasonal pastries, and tropical fruit turnovers.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Holey Grail Donuts","price":12,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"Show up right when they open as the rotating special flavors routinely sell out within an hour.","desc":"Kauai artisan donut shop making taro-based donuts with inventive tropical glazes and locally sourced ingredients.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kamehameha Bakery","price":5,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Bakery","tip":"The poi doughnuts are only available in limited quantities so aim to arrive before 7am.","desc":"Historic Honolulu bakery open since 1949, celebrated for its unique poi-glazed donuts and fresh Hawaiian bread.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg/800px-Belgium_2013_%2811620905224%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Rainbow Drive-In","price":10,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The mixed plate with gravy is the quintessential order that captures the full local plate lunch experience.","desc":"Iconic Honolulu drive-in open since 1961, serving classic plate lunches with two-scoop rice and macaroni salad.","photo":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-XCj0Y0xHStM?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"},
        {"name":"Zippy's Restaurants","price":12,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The chili plate is a Hawaii staple that has been a local comfort food since the 1960s.","desc":"Hawaii's beloved local chain serving comfort food plate lunches to generations of island families since 1966.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Grace's Inn","price":11,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The Korean chicken with kimchi is a local fusion favorite not commonly found on the mainland.","desc":"Long-standing Honolulu lunch spot serving generous Korean-inflected plate lunches popular with local workers.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"L&L Hawaiian Barbecue","price":11,"rating":4.4,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The BBQ mix plate allows you to sample both the chicken and beef in a single visit.","desc":"Hawaii's largest plate lunch chain, now with locations across the mainland, serving classic island-style barbecue.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Highway Inn Kaka'ako","price":16,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The laulau plate is the most authentically Hawaiian preparation on the menu and worth every bite.","desc":"Beloved local institution serving authentic Hawaiian plate lunches in a casual modern setting since 1947.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Mitsu-Ken Okazu-Ya","price":9,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The garlic chicken is the undisputed star — locals drive across town specifically for this dish.","desc":"Tiny takeout counter in Kalihi with a cult following for its crispy garlic chicken plate lunches.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"Hank's Haute Dogs","price":12,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The loco moco dog is a playful local fusion item that surprises and delights first-time visitors.","desc":"Kakaako hot dog shop with a local twist, blending classic plate lunch flavors into creative artisan dogs.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kono's Northshore","price":13,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The kalua pig burrito is a North Shore original fusion that blends plate lunch and Mexican flavors.","desc":"North Shore favorite combining Hawaiian plate lunch staples with creative wraps and burritos for hungry surfers.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg/800px-Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ono Hawaiian Foods","price":14,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Local Plate Lunch","tip":"The combination plate with poi, lomi salmon, and chicken long rice is the perfect sampler for newcomers.","desc":"Cash-only Kapahulu institution serving some of the most authentic traditional Hawaiian food on the island since 1964.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Marukame Udon Waikiki","price":10,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"Watch your udon being made fresh through the open kitchen window while you wait in line.","desc":"Waikiki's most popular udon counter, hand-rolling thick sanuki-style noodles to order for incredible value.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Imanas Tei","price":28,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"The nabeyaki udon hot pot is a warming centerpiece dish perfect for sharing on a cool evening.","desc":"Intimate Japanese izakaya in Honolulu serving exceptional nabeyaki udon and traditional Japanese small plates.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Doraku Sushi & Udon","price":20,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"The truffle dashi udon is a sophisticated upgrade that elevates the classic bowl to fine dining territory.","desc":"Upscale Japanese restaurant in Waikiki pairing fresh sushi with creative and classic udon preparations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Tsukiji Fish Market Restaurant","price":22,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"The seafood udon with fresh local fish elevates this Japanese classic with an island spin.","desc":"Japanese-style fish market restaurant in Honolulu known for seafood-topped udon bowls and fresh sashimi sets.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Yanagi Sushi & Udon","price":18,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"The combination udon and sushi set lunch is the best deal for a filling midday meal.","desc":"Established Honolulu Japanese restaurant serving dependable udon and sushi to loyal regulars since the 1980s.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Gyotaku Japanese Restaurant","price":20,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"The yaki udon stir-fried version with vegetables is an underrated off-menu item worth requesting.","desc":"Family-style Japanese restaurant in Honolulu beloved for hearty udon noodle soups and bento plate combinations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Nana's Green Tea Honolulu","price":14,"rating":4.4,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"Pair the cold zaru udon with a matcha latte for the most complete Japanese café experience.","desc":"Japanese green tea café chain serving cold and hot udon alongside matcha desserts and light Japanese fare.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Tokkuri-Tei","price":30,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"Ask the chef for off-menu seasonal udon specials which often feature rare Japanese ingredients.","desc":"Cozy Honolulu izakaya serving inventive Japanese small plates alongside carefully crafted udon and sake pairings.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Tenkaippin Ramen & Udon","price":16,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Udon","tip":"The rich tonkotsu udon is a rare find that bridges Japanese regional styles in one bowl.","desc":"Japanese chain restaurant in Honolulu known for its thick, rich broth options in both ramen and udon.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Kakeudon.jpg/800px-Kakeudon.jpg"},
        {"name":"Helena's Hawaiian Food","price":15,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The pipikaula short ribs are a rare Hawaiian specialty you will almost never find elsewhere.","desc":"James Beard Award-winning family restaurant in Honolulu serving rare traditional Hawaiian dishes for over 70 years.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Pioneer Saloon","price":13,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The teriyaki chicken plate is a standout value and the most-ordered item on the board.","desc":"Classic Maui plate lunch counter serving hearty local-style meals with rice and macaroni salad since 1969.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"Da Kitchen","price":14,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The loco moco with gravy is massive — split it if you are not extremely hungry.","desc":"Popular Maui plate lunch chain known for enormous portions of local comfort food at fair prices.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Tin Roof Maui","price":15,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"Sheldon Simeon's garlic noodles and pork belly plate is the dish that put this spot on the map.","desc":"Chef Sheldon Simeon's casual Maui counter serving inspired local plate lunches rooted in Filipino-Hawaiian traditions.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Cafe 100","price":10,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The mini loco moco combo lets you try multiple variations of this Hawaii original in one meal.","desc":"Hilo institution credited with inventing the loco moco, now serving dozens of creative variations since 1946.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Tanioka's Seafood & Catering","price":12,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The mixed plate with both the poke and the hot entrees is the best of both worlds.","desc":"Waipahu local institution famous for its combination of fresh poke and classic hot plate lunch items.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg/800px-Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kalapawai Market Kailua","price":14,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The fresh-made sandwiches and daily plate specials sell out early so plan for an 11am visit.","desc":"Historic neighborhood market in Kailua serving fresh daily plate lunches and artisan sandwiches to beach-goers.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Side Street Inn","price":20,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The famous fried pork chops and pan-fried noodles are the dishes that keep locals coming back.","desc":"Beloved Honolulu neighborhood bar and kitchen serving legendary late-night local plate lunch favorites since 1992.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg/800px-Hawaiian-dishes-01.jpg"},
        {"name":"Wailuku Restaurant","price":11,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Plate Lunch","tip":"The saimin bowl makes for a perfect lighter companion to the heavier plate lunch options.","desc":"No-frills Maui diner open for decades, serving working-class plate lunches with generous scoops and simple flavors.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Leoda's Kitchen and Pie Shop","price":14,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The banana cream pie is the most ordered dessert — get a whole pie to share if you have the group.","desc":"Olowalu roadside pie shop on Maui serving homestyle savory pies and decadent dessert pies with aloha.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Lattice_apple_pie.png/800px-Lattice_apple_pie.png"},
        {"name":"Broke Da Mouth Grindz","price":13,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The shepherd's pie with local beef is a crowd-pleaser that converts even the most reluctant comfort food skeptics.","desc":"Maui comfort food café known for savory pies and hearty local dishes that deliver on every visit.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Lattice_apple_pie.png/800px-Lattice_apple_pie.png"},
        {"name":"Grandma's Coffee House","price":12,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The homemade fruit pies rotate seasonally so always ask what they baked fresh that morning.","desc":"Upcountry Maui heirloom coffee farm café dishing up grandma-style fruit pies and comfort food since 1983.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Top_down_view_of_peach_pie_%28722379748%29.jpg/800px-Top_down_view_of_peach_pie_%28722379748%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"The Pineapple Café","price":15,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The pineapple upside-down cake dessert is a must and works wonderfully as a souvenir box.","desc":"Charming Oahu café celebrating the pineapple through creative comfort dishes and tropical baked desserts.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Top_down_view_of_peach_pie_%28722379748%29.jpg/800px-Top_down_view_of_peach_pie_%28722379748%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Hilo Bay Café","price":22,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The savory pot pie special on weekends is a hearty local-ingredient dish worth timing your trip around.","desc":"Waterfront Big Island restaurant blending island ingredients into refined American comfort food and savory pies.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg/800px-Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg"},
        {"name":"Café Pesto","price":25,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The wood-fired pizza with local goat cheese and Big Island mushrooms is a comforting island favorite.","desc":"Big Island bistro near the Hilo waterfront offering wood-fired comfort dishes with fresh island produce.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/80/ChickenpotpieswholeFeb09.jpg/800px-ChickenpotpieswholeFeb09.jpg"},
        {"name":"Punalu'u Sweetbread Comfort Kitchen","price":11,"rating":4.4,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The bread pudding made from their famous sweetbread is a comforting dessert you will want seconds of.","desc":"Big Island bakery-turned-café using their famous sweet bread as the base for warmly satisfying comfort desserts.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Top_down_view_of_peach_pie_%28722379748%29.jpg/800px-Top_down_view_of_peach_pie_%28722379748%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Koa Pancake House","price":14,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The macadamia nut pancakes with coconut syrup are an indulgent island comfort breakfast worth every calorie.","desc":"Neighborhood Honolulu breakfast spot serving fluffy island-inspired pancakes and old-fashioned comfort food daily.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg/800px-Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg"},
        {"name":"Over Easy Kaka'ako","price":16,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Pies & Comfort","tip":"The quiche of the day is made fresh every morning and sells out well before noon.","desc":"Trendy Honolulu brunch café serving artisan quiches, savory tarts, and creative comfort plates in an airy space.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Chicken_Noodle_Soup_US.jpg/800px-Chicken_Noodle_Soup_US.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ono Hawaiian Foods","price":14,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"Try the poi even if you are nervous — it is the starchy soul of traditional Hawaiian cuisine.","desc":"Kapahulu cash-only landmark serving deeply traditional Hawaiian food including poi, laulau, and lomi salmon since 1964.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Highway Inn Waipahu","price":15,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The combination plate with laulau, poi, and chicken long rice captures the full traditional experience.","desc":"The original Highway Inn location in Waipahu, preserving authentic Hawaiian recipes that date back to 1947.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kono's Hawaiian Kitchen","price":13,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"Ask for extra taro leaves with your laulau for an extra layer of earthy traditional flavor.","desc":"Family-operated Hawaiian kitchen in Kailua-Kona specializing in slow-cooked traditional dishes and daily fresh poi.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Haupia.jpg/800px-Haupia.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ai Love Nalo","price":12,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The kalo-based dishes reflect a deep commitment to indigenous Hawaiian food sovereignty and are extraordinary.","desc":"Waimanalo community restaurant focused on native Hawaiian ingredients, especially kalo, in traditional and modern preparations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Luaulau.png/800px-Luaulau.png"},
        {"name":"Helenas Hawaiian Food","price":15,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The pipikaula is only available in limited quantity and is the rarest traditional dish on the island.","desc":"James Beard Award-winning North King Street institution preserving rare traditional Hawaiian recipes across generations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Haili's Hawaiian Foods","price":11,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The fresh poi delivered on Tuesdays and Fridays is notably smoother and more flavorful on those days.","desc":"Hilo institution serving traditional Hawaiian food including kalua pig, poi, and haupia to locals and visitors.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Hukilau Lanai","price":35,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The Hawaiian tasting menu is the most complete introduction to traditional flavors available in a fine dining setting.","desc":"Kauai lagoon restaurant offering refined traditional Hawaiian dishes in a romantic waterfront setting with cultural storytelling.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Luaulau.png/800px-Luaulau.png"},
        {"name":"Tanioka's Hawaiian Food","price":12,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The squid luau is a traditional taro leaf dish that is both earthy and deeply satisfying.","desc":"West Oahu staple serving traditional Hawaiian plate combinations with laulau, haupia, and fresh kalo dishes.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Sam Sato's","price":10,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Traditional Hawaiian","tip":"The mochi dumplings sold at the counter make a perfect sweet finish to the savory traditional meal.","desc":"Maui family restaurant beloved for traditional Hawaiian food, saimin, and homemade mochi since the mid-20th century.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Sam Sato's Maui","price":9,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The dry mein with char siu pork is the off-menu order that devoted regulars know to get.","desc":"Wailuku legend serving the best saimin and dry mein noodles on Maui from a classic diner counter.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Classic_Saimin.jpg/800px-Classic_Saimin.jpg"},
        {"name":"Palace Saimin","price":8,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"Order extra wontons in your saimin — they are handmade daily and melt in your mouth.","desc":"Honolulu saimin institution serving hand-crafted noodle soup in a humble counter setting since 1946.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Classic_Saimin.jpg/800px-Classic_Saimin.jpg"},
        {"name":"Shiro's Saimin Haven","price":9,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The special saimin with fishcake, spam, and green onions is the true local version of this Hawaiian classic.","desc":"Aiea neighborhood icon serving Hawaii's signature saimin noodle soup and dry mein to three generations of locals.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Classic_Saimin.jpg/800px-Classic_Saimin.jpg"},
        {"name":"Hamura Saimin Stand","price":8,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The passion fruit lilikoi chiffon pie dessert is a Kauai institution — never leave without trying it.","desc":"Legendary Lihue counter open since 1952, serving Kauai's most famous saimin from the same recipe for decades.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ec/Shoyu_ramen%2C_at_Kasukabe_Station_%282014.05.05%29_1.jpg/800px-Shoyu_ramen%2C_at_Kasukabe_Station_%282014.05.05%29_1.jpg"},
        {"name":"Zippy's Saimin Station","price":10,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The dry mein bowl with extra chili paste is a satisfying late-night option available well past midnight.","desc":"Hawaii's beloved local chain offering consistent and comforting saimin and dry mein at all hours.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Nabeyaku_ramen_%28cropped%29.jpg/800px-Nabeyaku_ramen_%28cropped%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Nori's Saimin & Snacks","price":9,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The tempura udon-saimin hybrid is a creative innovation that long-time customers enthusiastically recommend.","desc":"Hilo neighborhood saimin shop serving hearty bowls with house-made broth and fresh noodles to loyal locals.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ec/Shoyu_ramen%2C_at_Kasukabe_Station_%282014.05.05%29_1.jpg/800px-Shoyu_ramen%2C_at_Kasukabe_Station_%282014.05.05%29_1.jpg"},
        {"name":"Masa & Joyce Saimin","price":8,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The wonton saimin with extra green onion is the most beloved order from the regulars here.","desc":"Old-school Honolulu saimin counter beloved by working locals for cheap, honest bowls of noodle soup.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Classic_Saimin.jpg/800px-Classic_Saimin.jpg"},
        {"name":"Masu's Massive Plate Lunches","price":10,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"Ask for the dry mein special with extra teriyaki beef for a hearty combination unique to this shop.","desc":"Big Island local favorite combining oversized plate lunches with classic saimin and dry mein noodle bowls.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Classic_Saimin.jpg/800px-Classic_Saimin.jpg"},
        {"name":"Waiola Saimin","price":9,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Saimin & Dry Mein","tip":"The loaded saimin topped with a fried egg is a filling meal on its own that locals love.","desc":"Community institution in Honolulu serving comforting bowls of saimin alongside shave ice for decades.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ec/Shoyu_ramen%2C_at_Kasukabe_Station_%282014.05.05%29_1.jpg/800px-Shoyu_ramen%2C_at_Kasukabe_Station_%282014.05.05%29_1.jpg"},
        {"name":"Heavenly Island Lifestyle","price":18,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The taro pancakes with mango compote are a uniquely Hawaiian brunch item not found anywhere on the mainland.","desc":"Waikiki health-forward brunch café blending Japanese and Hawaiian flavors into vibrant morning bowls and plates.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/20110703-24-brunch_spread_%285974097802%29.jpg/960px-20110703-24-brunch_spread_%285974097802%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Koko Head Café","price":20,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The Korean fried rice brunch bowl is a local legend — arrive by 9am or expect to wait.","desc":"Lee Anne Wong's celebrated Honolulu brunch spot fusing bold Asian flavors with Hawaii's freshest local ingredients.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/aa/Chips_with_ham_and_egg_at_Epping_Essex%2C_England.jpg/960px-Chips_with_ham_and_egg_at_Epping_Essex%2C_England.jpg"},
        {"name":"Café Coco Kauai","price":16,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"Ask to sit in the magical garden courtyard surrounded by tropical plants for the full Kauai ambiance.","desc":"Romantic Kauai garden café serving creative Asian-inspired brunch plates in a lush open-air tropical setting.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/King_prawn_starter_at_the_White_Hart_Inn%2C_Moreton%2C_Essex%2C_England.jpg/960px-King_prawn_starter_at_the_White_Hart_Inn%2C_Moreton%2C_Essex%2C_England.jpg"},
        {"name":"Egghead Café","price":15,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The kimchi scrambled eggs on taro toast is a uniquely local fusion dish you have to try.","desc":"Honolulu brunch café fusing Korean, Japanese, and Hawaiian breakfast traditions into creative egg-centered morning plates.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/King_prawn_starter_at_the_White_Hart_Inn%2C_Moreton%2C_Essex%2C_England.jpg/960px-King_prawn_starter_at_the_White_Hart_Inn%2C_Moreton%2C_Essex%2C_England.jpg"},
        {"name":"Mud Hen Water","price":22,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The Sunday brunch menu is more expansive than weekdays so plan your visit accordingly.","desc":"Kaimuki neighborhood restaurant celebrating Hawaii's multicultural identity through inventive Hawaiian-Asian fusion brunch plates.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/King_prawn_starter_at_the_White_Hart_Inn%2C_Moreton%2C_Essex%2C_England.jpg/960px-King_prawn_starter_at_the_White_Hart_Inn%2C_Moreton%2C_Essex%2C_England.jpg"},
        {"name":"Waikiki Yokocho","price":20,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The miso hollandaise eggs benedict is the fusion highlight of an inventive Asian-Hawaiian brunch menu.","desc":"Japanese izakaya alley concept in Waikiki blending classic American brunch with bold Japanese and Hawaiian flavors.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c6/Kells_Street_Kitchen_cheeseburger_Romford_outdoor_market_at_Market_Place_Romford_London_02.jpg/960px-Kells_Street_Kitchen_cheeseburger_Romford_outdoor_market_at_Market_Place_Romford_London_02.jpg"},
        {"name":"The Surfing Pig Hawaii","price":18,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The spam musubi benedict is a uniquely Hawaiian fusion brunch item that locals proudly champion.","desc":"Laid-back Honolulu brunch and bar playfully blending island comfort food with Asian fusion morning dishes.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/20110703-24-brunch_spread_%285974097802%29.jpg/960px-20110703-24-brunch_spread_%285974097802%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Sweet E's Café","price":14,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The ube pancakes are vibrant purple and taste as striking as they look on the plate.","desc":"Cheerful Honolulu brunch café known for colorful Filipino-Hawaiian fusion breakfast plates and creative ube specialties.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/30/Cheese_salad_roll_at_The_Original_Tea_Hut_at_High_Beach%2C_Essex%2C_England_01_lower_dynamic_range.jpg/960px-Cheese_salad_roll_at_The_Original_Tea_Hut_at_High_Beach%2C_Essex%2C_England_01_lower_dynamic_range.jpg"},
        {"name":"Morning Brew Kailua","price":15,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Asian Fusion Brunch","tip":"The green papaya salad with eggs is an unexpected Asian-fusion combo that brunch regulars rave about.","desc":"Kailua neighborhood café serving creative Asian-influenced brunch plates in a breezy open-air indoor-outdoor setting.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c6/Kells_Street_Kitchen_cheeseburger_Romford_outdoor_market_at_Market_Place_Romford_London_02.jpg/960px-Kells_Street_Kitchen_cheeseburger_Romford_outdoor_market_at_Market_Place_Romford_London_02.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kahumana Organic Farm Café","price":16,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"Everything on the menu is grown on the farm, so ask the server what was harvested that morning.","desc":"Waianae organic farm café serving Hawaiian plate lunches made entirely from ingredients grown steps away.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Da Poke Shack","price":14,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The spicy ahi plate with macaroni salad is the most-ordered combination and a genuine crowd-pleaser.","desc":"Kailua-Kona favorite combining fresh poke bowls with classic Hawaiian plate lunch sides in a simple beachside setting.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"South Shore Grill","price":15,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The kalua pork plate is slow-smoked for hours and worth every minute of the wait in line.","desc":"Kihei beach town lunch spot serving Hawaiian-style plate lunches grilled fresh with a backyard barbecue spirit.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kihei Caffe","price":13,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"Arrive by 7am on weekends to avoid the line that regularly wraps around the building.","desc":"Maui morning institution beloved by locals and surfers for generous Hawaiian plate lunches served all day.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"Aloha Mixed Plate","price":15,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The oceanfront picnic table seating with views of the Lahaina shoreline makes the meal twice as good.","desc":"Oceanfront Maui plate lunch restaurant offering traditional Hawaiian dishes with one of the island's best sunset views.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Big Island Grill Kona","price":14,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The breakfast plate with Portuguese sausage and eggs is a Big Island morning tradition worth experiencing.","desc":"Local Big Island favorite serving enormous Hawaiian plate lunches and breakfasts that keep regulars coming back daily.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Pono Market Kauai","price":11,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The chicken katsu plate is a perennial fan favorite that has not changed in recipe for thirty years.","desc":"Kapaa neighborhood market institution on Kauai serving legendary Hawaiian plate lunches from a well-worn deli counter.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg/800px-Loco_Moco_at_Ethel%27s_Grill%2C_Honolulu%2C_Hawaii.jpg"},
        {"name":"Yama's Fish Market","price":12,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The furikake salmon plate sells out fastest so order it as soon as you step through the door.","desc":"Honolulu fish market with a beloved plate lunch counter offering fresh fish plates and local poke combinations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1f/Roasted_puaa.jpg/800px-Roasted_puaa.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kua Aina Sandwich Shop","price":13,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Plate Lunch","tip":"The mahimahi burger with teriyaki sauce is the most Hawaiian item on the menu and a local icon.","desc":"North Shore Haleiwa legend turned multi-location chain, famous for thick burgers and fresh mahimahi sandwiches.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg/800px-Rainbow_Drive-In_mix_plate_lunch_%282194653288%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Teddy's Bigger Burgers","price":13,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"Build your own burger with a teriyaki pineapple topping for the most Hawaiian burger experience possible.","desc":"Hawaii-born burger chain known for thick hand-pattied burgers and local-style toppings at multiple island locations.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c1/2023_Night_Summit_%40_Pavilhao_Carlos_Lopes_TM1_0444_%2853335582229%29.jpg/960px-2023_Night_Summit_%40_Pavilhao_Carlos_Lopes_TM1_0444_%2853335582229%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kua Aina Burgers Haleiwa","price":14,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"The avocado bacon burger with their house sauce is the dish that made this North Shore spot famous.","desc":"Iconic Haleiwa burger shack credited with creating one of Hawaii's most celebrated and copied burgers since 1975.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c1/2023_Night_Summit_%40_Pavilhao_Carlos_Lopes_TM1_0444_%2853335582229%29.jpg/960px-2023_Night_Summit_%40_Pavilhao_Carlos_Lopes_TM1_0444_%2853335582229%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Mahaloha Burger","price":15,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"The taro bun option transforms any burger into an authentically Hawaiian island experience worth upgrading for.","desc":"Oahu burger joint serving creative local-inspired burgers with unique Hawaiian toppings and taro bun options.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Baconzilla_from_Checkers_%286710070177%29.jpg/960px-Baconzilla_from_Checkers_%286710070177%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"The Glazer's Plate","price":16,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"The malasada-glazed donut burger is a wild island creation that somehow manages to be completely delicious.","desc":"Creative Honolulu burger spot known for inventive toppings and Hawaiian-inspired glazes on house-smashed patties.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/...y_del_cielo_baj%C3%B3_La_Arepa..._-_Flickr_-_%C2%A1Fgz.jpg/960px-...y_del_cielo_baj%C3%B3_La_Arepa..._-_Flickr_-_%C2%A1Fgz.jpg"},
        {"name":"Big Kahuna's Burgers","price":13,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"The pineapple teriyaki glaze is the signature topping that keeps locals coming back to this roadside spot.","desc":"Casual Maui roadside burger stand grilling island-style patties with fresh pineapple and teriyaki for hungry beach-goers.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/20260314_Vkusno_i_Tochka_burger_%2816293%29.jpg/960px-20260314_Vkusno_i_Tochka_burger_%2816293%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"The Counter Burger Maui","price":18,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"The build-your-own option with local goat cheese and Big Island mushrooms is a premium island upgrade.","desc":"Maui craft burger restaurant offering premium build-your-own patties with locally sourced produce and artisan toppings.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Fisherman%E2%80%99s_Bistro%2C_Hamburger%2C_Finncanopus%2C_20240215_-_38.jpg/960px-Fisherman%E2%80%99s_Bistro%2C_Hamburger%2C_Finncanopus%2C_20240215_-_38.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ukulele's Burgers & Shakes","price":14,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"The macadamia nut milkshake paired with their signature local beef burger is the must-have combo.","desc":"Playful Kauai burger spot serving local grass-fed beef burgers and Hawaiian-flavored milkshakes in a bright open space.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b1/Detalle_de_hamburguesa_casera_con_pan%2C_carne%2C_jam%C3%B3n%2C_queso%2C_huevo_y_vegetales%2C_lista_para_consumir.jpg/960px-Detalle_de_hamburguesa_casera_con_pan%2C_carne%2C_jam%C3%B3n%2C_queso%2C_huevo_y_vegetales%2C_lista_para_consumir.jpg"},
        {"name":"Maui Brewing Co. Burger","price":20,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"Pair the brewer's burger with the Bikini Blonde lager for an ideal Hawaiian craft beer dinner.","desc":"Maui's beloved craft brewery serves elevated pub burgers featuring locally raised beef and house-brewed beer pairings.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Burger_on_plate.jpg/960px-Burger_on_plate.jpg"},
        {"name":"Lava Lava Beach Club Burger","price":22,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Burgers","tip":"Dine barefoot in the sand at sunset for the full beachside burger experience this Big Island spot delivers.","desc":"Big Island beachside bar and grill serving elevated burgers with your toes in the sand at Anaeho'omalu Bay.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/20260314_Vkusno_i_Tochka_burger_%2816293%29.jpg/960px-20260314_Vkusno_i_Tochka_burger_%2816293%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Peace Café Honolulu","price":14,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The vegan loco moco with mushroom gravy is a convincing plant-based take on Hawaii's most iconic dish.","desc":"Honolulu's beloved all-vegan café serving plant-based Hawaiian comfort food in a warm and welcoming community space.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Vegetarian_diet.jpg/800px-Vegetarian_diet.jpg"},
        {"name":"The Beet Box Café","price":15,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The açaí bowl topped with local honey and Kauai-grown fruit is the best on the island.","desc":"Hanalei health café on Kauai serving vegetarian and vegan bowls made with locally grown tropical produce.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Plant-Based_Dishes%2C_Raw_Food_%2829103285347%29.jpg/800px-Plant-Based_Dishes%2C_Raw_Food_%2829103285347%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Down to Earth Organic","price":12,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The hot bar changes daily so visit multiple times during your trip for a different meal each time.","desc":"Hawaii's beloved natural food store with a vegetarian hot bar serving organic prepared meals and fresh salads.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/94/Salad_platter.jpg/800px-Salad_platter.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ai Pono Café","price":16,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The taro burger with ulu breadfruit fries is a fully local plant-based meal worth seeking out.","desc":"Waimanalo café focusing on indigenous Hawaiian plant-based ingredients, promoting local farming and sustainable eating.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Plant-Based_Dishes%2C_Raw_Food_%2829103285347%29.jpg/800px-Plant-Based_Dishes%2C_Raw_Food_%2829103285347%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Café Haleiwa","price":13,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The garden veggie breakfast burrito is a surf-fueling morning staple among North Shore regulars.","desc":"North Shore surfer café in Haleiwa with a hearty vegetarian menu that has fed wave riders since 1985.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/94/Salad_platter.jpg/800px-Salad_platter.jpg"},
        {"name":"Hoku Foods Market","price":13,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The vegan poke bowl with hearts of palm is a convincing plant-based version of the island staple.","desc":"Honolulu natural foods market with an outstanding vegan-friendly deli counter stocking locally grown organic produce.","photo":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512621776951-a57141f2eefd?w=800&q=85"},
        {"name":"Greens & Vines","price":18,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The raw vegan Hawaiian plate with kale lomi and nut-based poi is a truly inventive dining experience.","desc":"Honolulu's pioneering raw vegan restaurant offering creative plant-based plates inspired by traditional Hawaiian flavors.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Vegetarian_diet.jpg/800px-Vegetarian_diet.jpg"},
        {"name":"Moku Roots","price":17,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The cauliflower kalua is so smoky and tender that meat eaters regularly order it without hesitation.","desc":"Maui's most celebrated plant-based restaurant serving locally grown vegan dishes inspired by Hawaiian culinary traditions.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Vegetarian_diet.jpg/800px-Vegetarian_diet.jpg"},
        {"name":"Roots Café Oahu","price":14,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Vegan/Vegetarian","tip":"The jackfruit pulled pork plate lunch is the best plant-based take on a local classic you will find.","desc":"Neighborhood Oahu vegan café crafting comfort food from whole plant ingredients with a firm local flavor identity.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Plant-Based_Dishes%2C_Raw_Food_%2829103285347%29.jpg/800px-Plant-Based_Dishes%2C_Raw_Food_%2829103285347%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Merriman's Maui","price":55,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The tasting menu showcases the best local ingredients — let the chef select your courses for a surprise.","desc":"Peter Merriman's Kapalua fine dining landmark pioneering Hawaii Regional Cuisine with locally sourced island ingredients.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg/800px-Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg"},
        {"name":"Alan Wong's Honolulu","price":65,"rating":4.9,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The two-way foie gras with taro is a signature dish that defines what elevated Hawaiian fusion means.","desc":"James Beard Award-winning chef Alan Wong's flagship restaurant defining the finest traditions of Hawaiian regional cuisine.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
        {"name":"Chef Mavro","price":75,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The wine pairing menu is curated to match Hawaii-grown ingredients with global varieties in extraordinary ways.","desc":"George Mavrothalassitis's James Beard Award-winning Honolulu restaurant creating French-Hawaiian fusion tasting menus of exceptional artistry.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
        {"name":"Vintage Cave Honolulu","price":180,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"This ultra-exclusive experience requires a reservation well in advance and offers one of Hawaii's most memorable meals.","desc":"Honolulu's most exclusive underground dining experience blending Japanese technique with the finest Hawaiian and global ingredients.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
        {"name":"Nobu Waikiki","price":70,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The new-style sashimi with local Hawaiian fish elevates Nobu's classic dish with incredible local ingredients.","desc":"Nobu Matsuhisa's Waikiki outpost serving Japanese-Peruvian fusion with abundant local Hawaiian fish and ingredients.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg/800px-Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg"},
        {"name":"MW Restaurant","price":50,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The dessert section is as thoughtfully crafted as the savory courses — never skip it.","desc":"Michelle Karr-Ueoka and Wade Ueoka's celebrated Honolulu restaurant showcasing modern Hawaii cuisine with soulful local ingredients.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
        {"name":"Senia","price":60,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The tasting menu format with locally foraged and farmed ingredients offers the most complete Senia experience.","desc":"Honolulu's innovative farm-to-table restaurant where chefs Chris Kajioka and Anthony Rush craft boundary-pushing Hawaiian fusion.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
        {"name":"Moku Kitchen","price":25,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"The wood-fired Hawaiian fusion pizza with kalua pork and caramelized pineapple is a must-order.","desc":"Kakaako wood-fire kitchen using local Hawaii ingredients to craft approachable Hawaiian fusion plates and pizzas.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Gobi_manchurian.jpg/800px-Gobi_manchurian.jpg"},
        {"name":"Lineage Lahaina","price":45,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Hawaiian Fusion","tip":"Chef Sheldon Simeon's personal family recipes here are more emotional and authentic than any TV moment.","desc":"Chef Sheldon Simeon's deeply personal Maui restaurant celebrating his Filipino-Hawaiian heritage through refined fusion cuisine.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg/800px-Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg"},
        {"name":"Ken's House of Pancakes","price":12,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The Portuguese sweet bread french toast is a Hilo institution that visitors always wish they had ordered first.","desc":"24-hour Hilo diner open since 1971, beloved by locals and late-night crowds for massive comfort breakfasts.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Strawberry_milk_shake_%28cropped%29.jpg/800px-Strawberry_milk_shake_%28cropped%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Boots & Kimo's Homestyle Kitchen","price":13,"rating":4.8,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The macadamia nut pancakes with their signature sauce are transcendent — no syrup required or desired.","desc":"Kailua neighborhood diner famous for its macadamia nut pancakes and lengthy weekend lines of devoted regulars.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/RedDot_Burger.jpg/800px-RedDot_Burger.jpg"},
        {"name":"Cinnamon's Restaurant Kailua","price":14,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The red velvet pancakes are an Instagram moment but the guava chiffon pancakes are the superior choice.","desc":"Beloved Kailua breakfast institution known for its outrageous pancake creations and warm, come-as-you-are diner atmosphere.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5a/Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif/lossy-page1-330px-Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif.jpg"},
        {"name":"Café 100 Hilo","price":9,"rating":4.7,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"Order several of the mini loco moco variations to sample this Big Island invention in its many forms.","desc":"The birthplace of the loco moco, serving this quintessential Hawaiian diner dish from the same Hilo corner since 1946.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5a/Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif/lossy-page1-330px-Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif.jpg"},
        {"name":"Kountry Kitchen Kauai","price":12,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The local-style fried rice with eggs and Portuguese sausage is the breakfast that fuels Kauai's working day.","desc":"Kapaa neighborhood diner on Kauai serving big-plate local breakfasts and lunches to regulars for over three decades.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5a/Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif/lossy-page1-330px-Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif.jpg"},
        {"name":"Puka Dog Hawaiian Style","price":11,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The lilikoi mustard with mango relish is the signature topping that makes this Kauai dog unforgettable.","desc":"Quirky Kauai Poipu diner famous for its unique vertical-toasted bun hot dogs stuffed with tropical fruit relishes.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/RedDot_Burger.jpg/800px-RedDot_Burger.jpg"},
        {"name":"Drive Inn Saimin Kauai","price":9,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The teriyaki beef stick is the perfect side that Kauai kids have been ordering since elementary school.","desc":"Classic Kauai drive-in diner serving no-frills local comfort food including saimin, burgers, and teriyaki plates.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5a/Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif/lossy-page1-330px-Collin%27s_Diner_%281942%29%2C_Route_7%2C_Canaan%2C_Connecticut_LCCN2017703366.tif.jpg"},
        {"name":"Wailuku Coffee Company","price":10,"rating":4.5,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The breakfast wrap with local eggs and fresh salsa makes a great portable meal for a hiking day.","desc":"Maui neighborhood café and diner serving no-fuss local breakfasts and lunches in the heart of old Wailuku Town.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Strawberry_milk_shake_%28cropped%29.jpg/800px-Strawberry_milk_shake_%28cropped%29.jpg"},
        {"name":"Over Easy Aina Haina","price":14,"rating":4.6,"cuisine":"Local Diner","tip":"The loco moco with extra gravy on the side for dipping is the order that regulars never deviate from.","desc":"Beloved Aina Haina neighborhood diner combining local comfort food traditions with fresh, quality ingredients daily.","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Strawberry_milk_shake_%28cropped%29.jpg/800px-Strawberry_milk_shake_%28cropped%29.jpg"}
